with version   stable 0.8.4
with version unstable 0.9.2
with base    SDL gst-plugins-base-0.10 libart_lgpl libmad liboil libsoup firefox
with elect   gimp '' '' for gimp plugin
with also    --enable-static=no
with role    video/player
with trait   library
with source    stable http://swfdec.freedesktop.org/download/swfdec/${VERSION:0:3}/swfdec-$VERSION.tar.gz
with source  unstable http://swfdec.freedesktop.org/download/swfdec/${VERSION:0:3}/swfdec-$VERSION.tar.gz
with info    good 20120710
with info    last 20081221
with info    vurl http://swfdec.freedesktop.org/wiki/
with info    home http://swfdec.freedesktop.org/wiki/
with info    cite 'flash animation and game rendering library
swfdec is a library for rendering Flash animations and games.
It was originally designed to be used for creating Flash
plugins for GStreamer, but is a fully standalone library
that only requires the libart library for drawing.
It includes a GTK+ player (swf_play) '

build(){
export LDFLAGS+=' -Wl,-rpath,/usr/lib/mozilla'
